Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.62,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:35.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:40.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:47.06,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:52.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.77,0:00:58.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever, I take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:06.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it’s not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:16.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:21.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard someone else’s biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.55,0:01:25.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn’t there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:30.81,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to gather up all our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.83,0:01:36.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search of something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:42.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:48.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:52.79,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.11,0:01:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.73,0:02:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sogeking!\N--There's no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... He couldn't have... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You called?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't you guys have\Nthe kindness to catch a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,making a desperate jump\Noff of the rooftop?! Morons!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an escort ship on the\Nother side of the bridge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.07,0:03:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that is the key to our escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like stealing that ship\Nis our only chance of surviving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Convert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky Centaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although your physical ability\Nindeed spikes, exceeding its limits,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your physical strength itself just can't\Nkeep up with that intensification.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not really smart.\NYou're shortening your life, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better than losing all sorts\Nof things right before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.99,0:04:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too ambitious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That naive idea of yours that you\Ncan save everyone and escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how far it gets you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behind the fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can see the outline of the ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, don't run away! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here! They're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fleet of battleships!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Buster Call has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Can't Protect Anyone Unless I Win!\NThird Gear Activated!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat. Our targets are Straw Hat Luffy\Nand his gang of about sixty pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely destroy Enies Lobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that, you guys! Don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? The battleships are ignoring\Nthe bridge--they aren't attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. My old man said it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the indiscriminate cannon fire avoided him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the bridge the criminal\NNico Robin is on is an exception for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Look at this! This bridge is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm the Chief of CP9!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.02,0:07:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a crazy sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Hey, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exercising a Buster Call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence concerted fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're targeting everything on Ohara,\Nthe island of archaeology.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilate the devils living in Ohara!\NIn the name of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buster Call...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merciless, indiscriminate cannon fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It destroys anything and everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hellfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tragedy is... That grisly event is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...happening again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry, you guys! Be quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop bossing us around, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I may say one more thing,\Nthis is affecting my wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you carry me a little more softly?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask too much! Besides,\Nyou're contradicting yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the price I paid for my great work,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's no exaggeration to say that\NI have wounds all over my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! All my ribs got broken! All six of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more than that, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, would you like to know\Nthe secret of my new weapon, Kabuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall explain it for you. Kabuto,\Nthe weapon that belongs to Sogeking, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sparkle!\N--Shut up, you jerk! Or we'll make you run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Spare me! My ribs\Ngot broken! A-All ten of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There are more than that.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then 20... 30?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about 100?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that cannon fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy sure does put on a big show.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing! Cannon fire! Cannon fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they aren't festival fireworks, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where's Luffy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, pirate lady, that iron\Ndoor we came through...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate guy broke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was amazing... though he became small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Small? Luffy did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are the ones, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm heading there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! How come you're small now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Gear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He opened the iron doors and\Nbecame small? What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must've been fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, Grandma! That pirate guy is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not making any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's hurry and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Grandma, I can hear something down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to stop here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it is,\Nwe just have to keep on going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go resolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! You're cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there water?! What?!\NWhy?! We have no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether there's someone in the passage or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one can now reach this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon this room will be submerged in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo coo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is located above the sea.\NThe seawater won't reach here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo coo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hear the sounds of the\Nbattleships' cannon fire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:14:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your pirate crew...\NWhat happened to Nico Robin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.24,0:14:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna go rescue them, go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take my focus off of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what they're going through\Nright now, they'll survive for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I let you get away now,\Nyou'll go kill my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take my focus off of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cannon attack has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I can hear a\Nstrange sound ahead of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, I sense something odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say this, but unlike you two,\NI'm delicate and cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And my sense is telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this sound is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.38,0:16:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ribs got broken again! Wait up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm severely injured with\Nbroken bones all over my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.55,0:16:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?! Hurry up and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a high caliber, befitting a boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like for a certain idiot to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder... if your abilities are\Ngood enough to back up that decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The result will be the same if you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Capture Nico Robin already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once this is all over, I'll be able\Nto become the world's hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Buster Call sounds like a gun salute for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Razor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finger Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tempest Kick! Leopard Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really defeat me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't protect anyone unless I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rifle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body. Empty Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.73,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Razor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:19:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you credit for having the guts to\Npick a fight with the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, you're just like any other pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.78,0:19:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems your level is nowhere\Nnear enough to put up a good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying Finger Pistol...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:20:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three Picks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying Finger Pistol...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was able to meet a man\Nwith some backbone. How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:21:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you run out of strength from\Nyour doping earlier after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's backbone you want, I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...another tactic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third... Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power that moves\Nfrom one bone to another...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.03,0:21:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look! My left arm is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the arm of a giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all show, don't even bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.07,0:22:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice would never surrender to evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if there's a soldier\Nwho can't protect what he should,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that alone is a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I do is in the name of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past... and in the future, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.69,0:22:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shivering Past! Dark Justice and Rob Lucci"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
